Key to genera allied to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="A. Camus" authorityYear="1950" box="[412,611,1944,1971]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Parahyparrhenia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
